_sText:
This is currently a demo map. Later I will work on expansion (adding  -3rd floor with trains and platforms and other NON SYMMETRICAL paths). Environment sound and additional plant zone (bomb B) will be included in the next patch.
For those who are into story lines and stuff - there is no story yet. But I placed a lot of cash in the bomb plant zone to make it look like there is some sort of a story.
